1. go to Active Directory
2. Open Server Manager App
3. Go to Tools (upper right hand corner of the Server Manager App)
4. Click on DNS
5. The DNS Manager App will open, and expand WIN-AD, Forward Lookup Zones and then right click on grayhats.local
6. Select New Host (A or AAAA)...
7. Fill in the "Name" field and "IP Address" field and click "Add Host" button on the bottom of the dialog box.



